<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.92.85967.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Dorsal and lateral habitus of Arastichus gallicola lectotype (female on the top left), along with three paralectotypes on the same pin." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/736463" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.92.85967.figure4-5>
    dc:description "Figure 4 - 5. Lateral habitus of Arastichus gallicola 4 female 5 male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/736464" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.92.85967.figure6-7>
    dc:description "Figure 6 - 7. Lateral habitus of Arastichus capipunctata 6 holotype female 7 paratype male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/736465" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.92.85967.figure8-9>
    dc:description "Figure 8 - 9. Lateral habitus of Arastichus gibernau 8 holotype female 9 paratype male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/736466" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.92.85967.figure10-15>
    dc:description "Figure 10 - 15. Arastichus gallicola 10 frontal view of head 11 posterior view of head 12 dorsal view of head 13 anterolateral view of head 14 female antenna 15 male antenna." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/736467" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.92.85967.figure16-20>
    dc:description "Figure 16 - 20. Arastichus gallicola 16 dorsal view of mesosoma 17 ventral view of mesosoma 18 ventral view of female metasoma 19 lateral view of female metasoma 20 propodeum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/736468" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.92.85967.figure21-25>
    dc:description "Figure 21 - 25. Arastichus capipunctata 21 frontal view of head 22 dorsal view of head 23 dorsal view of mesosoma, arrow pointing to the bilobed posterior margin of mesoscutum 24 - 25 Arastichus gibernau 24 frontal view of head 25 lateral view of mesosoma, arrow pointing to the circular fossa on the posterior corner of metapleuron." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/736469" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.92.85967.figure26>
    dc:description "Figure 26. Female genitalia of Arastichus spp. based on photographs of slide-mounted specimens. Morphological variations are evident among species and within species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/736470" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.92.85967.figure27>
    dc:description "Figure 27. Male genitalia of Arastichus spp. based on photographs of slide-mounted specimens. Dsp digital spine; Aed aedeagus; Dqt digitus; Dsp d igital spine; Phl phallobase; Prm paramere; Vsl volsella." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/736471" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.92.85967.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Illustration of the lifecycle of Arastichus gallicola with its host plant, Thaumatophyllum solimoesense (Arecaceae). Illustrated by Taina Litwak." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/736461" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

